Release Checklist
=================
* Set Constants.DEBUG to false
* Make sure dex is set to non optimised

General Workflow
================
```
    git checkout glimmr-l
    git cherry-pick master..dev
    # Bump AndroidManifest.xml to $version
    git commit -am "Bump version for release"
    git tag ${version}-l

    git checkout master
    git cherry-pick master..dev
    # Bump AndroidManifest.xml to $version
    git commit -am "Bump version for release"
    git tag ${version}-free

    git checkout dev
    git cherry-pick dev..master
    git push --all
    git push --tags
```
